Sunsets seem eternal. They're warm, passionate, bloody, and violent; forever relative to a person's eyes.

They are gateways to darkness and terror, at the same time, a beautiful grandeur of moonlit streets and twinkling starlight. 
Forever innocent and broken, will the clouds bathed in blood ever be.

What does the crimson fading light mean to you?

The more bonkers, the more timeless. Hands up who doesn't love a statement jacket? I collect them, one a year and they last forever (ok when I say forever my oldest is nine years old which makes it vintage in my book) Have blogged the contenders for this year. There is nothing I like better over a plain tee and jeans for immediate transformation into out out garb (dear autocorrect. When I write out out, PLEASE stop changing it to put out 😱😱😫😝😝😂) Only thing is that they do all seem to be round neck boxy style which I can't imagine is universally flattering?! Any others I should be looking at, let me know! Thanking you kindly. Link in bio #newblogpost #outout #statement #jacket #ipromiseyouitsaninvestment #fashion #fblogger
